Container.Overview:
 This tool will continuosly run Speedtests at the chosen interval and export the data to InfluxDB. &lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
# What makes this different is that it's using the Ookla CLI tool which provides some expanded details that you can use to tag your Influx Data. &lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
An example of the dashboard I made in Grafana can be found at https://grafana.com/grafana/dashboards/13053. &lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;strong&gt; This container only includes the scripts to run the speedtests and export to Influx. InfluxDB must be installed seperatly. I welcome feedback or additional improvements. Please open an issue on the project page. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;
